<template>
  <v-app id="inspire">
    <NavBarProfile/>
    <v-main class="grey lighten-3">
      <ProfileInfo/>
    </v-main>
  </v-app>
</template>

<script>
  import NavBarProfile from '../components/NavBarProfile.vue'
  import ProfileInfo from '../components/ProfileInfo.vue'
  import axios from 'axios';
  
  export default {
    data() {
      return {
        user: null,
      }
    },
    components: {
      NavBarProfile,
      ProfileInfo,
    },
    methods: {
      fetchUser() {
        axios.get('http://localhost:3000/user/utente1')
        .then(({data}) => {  // descrutoring data
          this.user = data
          console.log(this.user)
        })
        .catch(error => {
          console.log(error)
        })
      },
    },
    mounted
  }
</script>
